%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20ingenious%20way%20your%20credit%20card%20company%20is%20making%20your%20life%20easier%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Golden%20credit%20card%20tapping%20a%20blue%20terminal%20with%20emojis%20(money%20bag%2C%20green%20heart%2C%20exclamation%20points%2C%20and%20floating%20money)%20rotating%20on%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663b9a36b4abc992e8c6e412%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBanks%20and%20credit-card%20companies%20are%20getting%20better%20at%20discerning%20which%20payments%20are%20fraudulent%20and%20which%20are%20legit.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-March%2C%20a%20scammer%20in%20California%20tried%20to%20buy%20%24150%20worth%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-wingstop-first-time-review-photos-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWingstop%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20my%20debit%20card.%20Aside%20from%20being%20impressed%20at%20the%20sheer%20size%20of%20the%20order%2C%20I%20was%20relieved%20because%20Citibank%2C%20which%20issued%20my%20card%2C%20declined%20the%20transaction%20on%20the%20spot%20and%20alerted%20me%20to%20the%20fraud.%20In%20minutes%20I%20was%20able%20to%20shut%20off%20my%20card%2C%20heading%20off%20any%20more%20purchases%20by%20the%20scammers%2C%20and%20order%20a%20new%20card.%20All's%20well%20that%20ends%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20went%20to%20Buenos%20Aires%20in%20April%2C%20I%20figured%20I%20might%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhy-was-my-credit-card-declined%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erun%20into%20a%20similar%20situation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sure%2C%20the%20banks%3Cem%3E%20say%3C%2Fem%3E%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20call%20ahead%20when%20you%20travel%20anymore%2C%20but%20I%20assumed%20I'd%20still%20have%20some%20purchase%20flagged%20as%20potential%20fraud%2C%20as%20had%20happened%20in%20past%20trips%20abroad.%20Miraculously%2C%20everything%20went%20off%20without%20a%20hitch.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20knew%20that%20I%20%3Cem%3Ewould%3C%2Fem%3E%20spend%20%24200%20on%20Botox%20in%20Argentina%2C%20but%20it%20did.%20(No%2C%20I%20didn't%20book%20my%20flight%20on%20the%20same%20card%2C%20and%20whatever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotox-injections-fillers-plastic-surgery-gen-z-social-media-filters-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeverybody%20gets%20Botox%20now%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20great%20that%20banks%20and%20credit-card%20companies%20are%20getting%20better%20at%20discerning%20which%20payments%20are%20fraudulent%20and%20which%20are%20legit.%20Many%20people%20have%20some%20horror%20story%20about%20having%20their%20credit%20card%20stolen%20or%20having%20their%20own%20legitimate%20transactions%20flagged%20as%20suspicious.%20And%20it's%20nice%20not%20to%20have%20to%20spend%2020%20minutes%20on%20the%20phone%20before%20a%20vacation%20explaining%20where%20you're%20going%20and%20when.%20Credit-card%20fraud%20protection%20is%20still%20far%20from%20perfect%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20technology%20is%20improving.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20it's%20also%20kind%20of%20wild%20to%20consider%20just%20how%20much%20financial%20institutions%20must%20know%20about%20you%20to%20make%20the%20right%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20curious%20about%20how%20it%20all%20works%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20frankly%2C%20a%20little%20creeped%20out.%20So%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20some%20credit-card%20companies%20and%20academics%20to%20learn%20more.%20Why%20don't%20people%20have%20to%20alert%20their%20credit-card%20companies%20about%20travel%20anymore%3F%20And%2C%20more%20broadly%2C%20just%20how%20have%20banks%20gotten%20so%20good%20at%20figuring%20out%20what's%20normal%20about%20our%20spending%20habits%20and%20what%20isn't%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20receives%20thousands%20of%20card-fraud%20complaints%20each%20year.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnilsonreport.com%2Fnewsletters%2F1254%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENilson%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20tracks%20the%20card%20industry%2C%20says%20payment-card%20fraud%20resulted%20in%20%2433%20billion%20in%20losses%20worldwide%20in%202022%20and%20%2413.6%20billion%20in%20losses%20in%20the%20US.%20As%20such%2C%20credit-card%20issuers%20and%20banks%20are%20keen%20to%20do%20what%20they%20can%20to%20spot%20fraud.%20They%20want%20to%20keep%20their%20customers%20happy%2C%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20they%20want%20to%20stem%20their%20losses.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20major%20credit-card%20issuers%20and%20banks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-card-lost-stolen-what-to-do%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerally%20have%20a%20zero-liability%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20that%20when%20a%20customer%20gets%20scammed%2C%20the%20organization%2C%20not%20the%20customer%2C%20has%20to%20eat%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20ago%2C%20whether%20a%20transaction%20went%20through%20was%20based%20on%20things%20like%20whether%20a%20physical%20card%20was%20present%2C%20whether%20you%20had%20enough%20money%20to%20make%20the%20purchase%2C%20and%20(if%20the%20cashier%20wanted%20to%20look)%20whether%20your%20signature%20on%20the%20receipt%20matched%20the%20one%20on%20the%20back%20of%20your%20card.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20cashier%20may%20have%20even%20asked%20for%20ID%20or%20called%20the%20bank%20to%20verify%20the%20funds.%20We've%20come%20a%20long%20way%20from%20those%20bad%20old%20days%20by%20using%20the%20same%20tools%20that%20power%20most%20innovations%3A%20data%20and%20computers.%20Credit-card%20companies%20and%20banks%20know%20%3Cem%3Ea%20lot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20us%20%E2%80%94%20where%20we%20shop%2C%20when%20we%20spend%2C%20and%20how%20much%20we're%20usually%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20things%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20getting%20better%20and%20better%20at%20turning%20that%20knowledge%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-exaggeration-openai-nvidia-microsoft-chatgpt-jobs-investors-markets-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20the%20rage%20to%20talk%20about%20newfangled%20forms%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fraud%20detection%20owes%20a%20lot%20to%20machine%20learning%2C%20a%20field%20within%20AI%20that's%20been%20around%20for%20years.%20A%20bunch%20of%20data%20gets%20dumped%20into%20computer%20systems%2C%20and%20algorithms%20figure%20out%20patterns%20and%20relationships.%20The%20algorithms%20create%20decision%20trees%20to%20predict%20the%20likelihood%20of%20different%20outcomes%20and%20identify%20what%20may%20be%20considered%20normal%20or%20fishy.%20It's%20not%20that%20your%20credit-card%20company%20knows%20that%20you%2C%20specifically%2C%20would%20blow%20a%20bunch%20of%20cash%20on%20A%20and%20not%20on%20B%20%E2%80%94%20it%20knows%20that%20customers%20with%20your%20profile%20are%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Blikes%20A%26quot%3B%20camp%20and%20not%20the%20%26quot%3Blikes%20B%26quot%3B%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20looking%20at%20what's%20happening%20that%20is%20very%20much%20out%20of%20the%20ordinary%20for%20your%20general%20behaviors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tina%20Eide%2C%20an%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20global%20fraud%20risk%20at%20American%20Express.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20I%20talk%20about%20general%20behaviors%2C%20it%20is%20generalized%2C%20right%3F%20It%20is%20not%20down%20to%20the%20specific%20purchase%20or%20to%20the%20specific%20merchant.%26quot%3B%20Eide%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20models%20are%20evaluating%20a%20trillion%20dollars'%20worth%20of%20transactions%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20machines%20know%20more%20now%20than%20ever.%20Mike%20Lemberger%2C%20Visa's%20regional%20risk%20officer%20for%20North%20America%2C%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20the%20number%20of%20data%20points%20people%20generate%20with%20their%20credit%20cards%20has%20grown%20tremendously.%20People%20are%20increasingly%20using%20cards%20over%20cash.%20And%20they%20don't%20just%20have%20a%20physical%20card%20they're%20pulling%20out%20at%20the%20store%20%E2%80%94%20they've%20got%20their%20card%20credentials%20in%20their%20Amazon%20account%2C%20Netflix%20account%2C%20iPhone%2C%20etc.%20The%20more%20purchases%20the%20card%20issuer%20can%20analyze%2C%20the%20more%20accurate%20the%20fraud%20detection%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVisa%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20consumer%20information%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20your%20financial%20institution%20that%20has%20that%20%E2%80%94%20but%20what%20we%20have%20is%20this%20triangulation%20of%20all%20these%20data%20points%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemberger%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20create%20more%20and%20better%20scores%2C%20layer%20on%20top%20of%20that%20machine%20learning%20and%20AI%20abilities%2C%20and%20it%20becomes%20a%20much%2C%20much%20more%20powerful%20predictor%2C%20which%20we%20then%20feed%20into%20all%20of%20our%20partners%20to%20say%2C%20'Hey%20guys%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20make%20the%20best%20decisions%2C%20here's%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20really%20good%20information.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisa%20isn't%20going%20to%20block%20your%20card%20directly%2C%20but%20it'll%20alert%20your%20bank%20that%20your%20purchase%20looks%20suspicious%20or%20that%20fraud%20has%20been%20detected%20at%20the%20merchant%20you're%20dealing%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20all%20seemed%20pretty%20simple%20until%20I%20talked%20to%20Yann-A%C3%ABl%20Le%20Borgne%20and%20Gianluca%20Bontempi%2C%20a%20pair%20of%20researchers%20at%20the%20Universit%C3%A9%20Libre%20de%20Bruxelles%20in%20Belgium%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffraud-detection-handbook.github.io%2Ffraud-detection-handbook%2FForeword.html%23authors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20on%20machine%20learning%20and%20card%20fraud%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20emphasized%20the%20vast%20scale%20of%20this%20fraud-detection%20technology.%20Companies%20and%20their%20algorithms%20are%20ingesting%20millions%20of%20transactions%20and%20creating%20so%20many%20decision%20trees%20to%20categorize%20certain%20activities%20that%20it%20can%20defy%20human%20logic%2C%20they%20said.%20Basically%2C%20the%20computer%20may%20be%20right%20that%20your%20transaction%20looks%20funky%20even%20if%20it's%20made%20in%20your%20home%20city%20at%20a%20fairly%20innocuous%20vendor%2C%20or%20it%20may%20be%20right%20that%20the%20transaction%20is%20fine%20even%20though%20it's%20made%20in%20a%20faraway%20place%20%E2%80%94%20but%20when%20humans%20try%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20did%20or%20didn't%20sound%20the%20alarm%2C%20nobody%20will%20really%20be%20able%20to%20pinpoint%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMachines%20can%20consider%20many%20more%20features%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20it's%20not%20clear%20if%20all%20those%20features%20have%20meaning%20for%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20Bontempi%20said.%20%26quot%3BHumans%20are%20used%20to%20working%20with%20two%2C%20three%20features%2C%20at%20most%20five%20features%2C%20while%20machines%20can%20work%20with%20hundreds%20of%20features.%20So%20there%20are%20really%20different%20levels%20between%20what%20a%20machine%20can%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20human-written%20rules%2C%20which%20are%20generally%20interpretable%2C%20and%20there%20are%20machine-written%20rules%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20black%20box.%20They're%20more%20accurate%2C%20but%20they%20may%20be%20harder%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%2C%20for%20people%20to%20reverse%20engineer.%20And%20banks%20may%20be%20using%20several%20different%20algorithms%2C%20making%20this%20even%20more%20complicated.%20Data%20scientists%20are%20the%20ultimate%20decision-makers%2C%20but%20the%20information%20they're%20dealing%20with%20is%20based%20on%20highly%20complex%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20explained%20to%20experts%20my%20somewhat%20embarrassing%20wings-versus-wrinkles%20conundrum%20and%20asked%20what%20may%20have%20triggered%20one%20alert%20and%20not%20the%20other%2C%20they%20offered%20up%20different%20explanations.%20Eide%2C%20from%20American%20Express%2C%20said%20that%20even%20though%20I%20hadn't%20booked%20my%20trip%20to%20Argentina%20with%20the%20credit%20card%20I%20used%20to%20buy%20the%20Botox%2C%20something%20else%20had%20probably%20tipped%20off%20the%20system%20that%20I%20was%20there.%20I%20realized%20I'd%20also%20bought%20a%20package%20of%20spin%20classes%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%20on%20my%20phone%20with%20the%20same%20card.%20I%20had%20also%20paid%20for%20a%20meal%20in%20the%20city.%20Lemberger%2C%20from%20Visa%2C%20emphasized%20that%20it's%20about%20all%20the%20data%20and%20spending%20patterns%20and%20said%20that%20given%20my%20spending%20patterns%2C%20the%20Botox%20likely%20matched%20my%20profile%20more%20than%20the%20massive%20delivery%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hate%20to%20say%20this%20to%20you%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20all%20these%20data%20points%20build%20personas.%20Just%20like%20in%20marketing%20somebody%20would%20use%20personas%20to%20market%20to%20you%2C%20we're%20using%20that%20same%20technology%20to%20protect%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20we%20use%20those%20data%20points%20to%20not%20just%20secure%20you%20but%20the%20whole%20ecosystem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%20it%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20the%20supercomputers%20that%20credit-card%20companies%20and%20banks%20are%20working%20with%20could%20know%20more%20about%20me%20than%20I%20even%20know%20or%20understand%20about%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20probable%20that%20the%20exact%20reason%20why%20a%20transaction%20caused%20your%20card%20to%20be%20blocked%20has%20no%20straightforward%20interpretation%2C%26quot%3B%20Le%20Borgne%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20asked%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20credit-card%20protections%20and%20debit%20protections%20and%20was%20told%20not%20really%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20banks%20will%20be%20a%20little%20more%20restrictive%20about%20credit%20because%20they're%20technically%20lending%20you%20money%20that's%20not%20limited%20by%20your%20actual%20cash%20balance.%20I%20also%20asked%20if%20companies%20don't%20worry%20about%20preclearing%20travel%20because%20they%20don't%20care%20as%20much%20about%20losing%20money%20to%20fraud%20anymore%2C%20to%20which%20the%20answer%20was%20a%20hard%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20somebody's%20got%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20fraudulent%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemberger%20said.%20Credit-card%20companies%20will%20give%20you%20your%20money%20back%20if%20you're%20a%20victim%20of%20fraud%2C%20but%20they'll%20find%20another%20place%20to%20recoup%20that%20money%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-late-fees-cap-swipe-mastercard-visa-jpmorgan-rewards-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%20as%20they%20always%20do%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstinctually%2C%20I%20am%20not%20a%20technology-is-awesome%20person%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20AI%20really%20is%20going%20to%20kill%20us%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20we%20should%20unplug%20it.%20I'm%20not%20super%20freaked%20out%20about%20the%20privacy%20stuff%2C%20but%20I%20also%20don't%20love%20the%20idea%20that%20AmEx%20and%20JPMorgan%20and%20Citi%20have%20me%20so%20pegged.%20But%20it's%20cool%20that%20companies%20really%20are%20making%20fraud%20detection%20better%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20world%20where%20fraudsters%20themselves%20are%20constantly%20getting%20better.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20like%20%26quot%3BYay%2C%20banks!%26quot%3B%20but%20maybe%20here%20the%20answer%20really%20is%20a%20little%20%26quot%3BYay%2C%20banks!%26quot%3B%20At%