of%20a%20bag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633b1760dfb1341e901c3a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EeasyJet%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20matched%20up%20at%20the%20airport's%20sizer.%20I%20couldn't%20find%20one%20for%20Wizz%2C%20but%20its%20limit%20is%20slightly%20smaller%20at%2040%20x%2030%20x%2020cm.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rucksack%20placed%20inside%20an%20easyJet%20bag%20sizer%20at%20an%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663b98d6b4abc992e8c6e33b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222814%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20I%20was%20disappointed%20to%20see%20just%20how%20tiny%20Ryanair's%20limit%20is%3A%2040%20x%2020%20x%2025cm.%20My%20bag%20still%20squeezed%20into%20the%20sizer%2C%20but%20I'd%20already%20paid%20an%20extra%20%C2%A324%20(%2430)%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20I%20wouldn't%20face%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%2070%20euros%20(%2475).%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20rucksack%20in%20a%20Ryanair%20bag%20sizer%20at%20the%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310a20ec0c696569ff19ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERyanair's%20free%20carry-on%20size%20is%20also%20smaller%20than%20US%20budget%20carriers%20like%20Frontier%2C%20Spirit%2C%20Allegiant%2C%20and%20Southwest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20boarding%2C%20the%20staff%20didn't%20seem%20to%20care%20how%20big%20anyone's%20bag%20was%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20looked%20much%20larger%20than%20mine.%20I%20didn't%20risk%20it%20because%20Business%20Insider%20paid%20for%20the%20f