img%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20boarding%20screen%20for%20Roma-Fco%20displayed%20for%20a%20Wizz%20flight%20at%20Madrid%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663b9ace9686a6f37bfd372d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWizz%20was%20named%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.which.co.uk%2Freviews%2Fairlines%2Farticle%2Fbest-and-worst-airlines-a5EhC8N851et%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworst%20short-haul%20airline%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20survey%20published%20in%20February%20by%20Which%3F%2C%20a%20British%20consumer%20advocacy%20group.%20It%20said%2044%25%20of%20passengers%20reported%20some%20kind%20of%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20heard%20bad%20stories%20from%20friends%20about%20Wizz%20cancellations.%20Last%20summer%2C%20my%20roommate%20had%20his%20flight%20home%20canceled%20twice%2C%20and%20it%20took%20him%20several%20attempts%20to%20get%20his%20money%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20Wizz%20and%20easyJet%2C%20I%20boarded%20via%20a%20jet%20bridge%2C%20whereas%20Ryanair%20has%20steps%20built%20into%20its%20planes%20to%20save%20time%20between%20flights%2C%20and%20minimize%20costs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passengers%20boarding%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%20at%20Stansted%20Airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310aa6ec0c696569ff1a1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tracked%20the%20Boeing%20737-800%20on%20Flightradar24%20and%20saw%20that%20boarding%20opened%20at%20my%20gate%20almost%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20touched%20down%20at%20London%20Stansted%20Airport%2C%20leaving%20the%20crew%20with%20little%20time%20between%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv