0on%20the%20overhead%20lockers.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cabin%20of%20a%20Ryanair%20Boeing%20737-800%20in%20its%20yellow%20and%20blue%20color%20scheme%20with%20commercials%20on%20the%20overhead%20bins%2C%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20aisle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66310c2310dfcda40964d9ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20easyJet%20Airbus%20A319%20I%20flew%20on%20was%2013%20years%20old%2C%20so%20the%20interior%20looked%20dated%2C%20although%20I%20thought%20the%20seats'%20moquette%20pattern%20was%20fun%20without%20being%20overbearing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cabin%20of%20an%20easyJet%20A319%20as%20pictured%20from%20the%20aisle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663b9c0ff27898f532d50709%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWizz%20Air%20had%20the%20most%20modern%20plane%20of%20the%20bunch%2C%20a%2014-month-old%20Airbus%20A321neo%20fitted%20in%20its%20latest%20interior%20with%20blue%20leather%20seats.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cabin%20of%20a%20Wizz%20Air%20Airbus%20A320neo%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20aisle%20looking%20forward%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663b9d039686a6f37bfd388a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20Syme%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAll%20of%20the%20airlines%20are%20no-frills%20so%20there%20were%20no%20plug%20sockets%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20seats%20reclined.%20I%20was%20comfiest%20on%20board%20Wizz%2C