0Trump%20voter%20proved%20the%20MyPillow%20Guy%20wrong.%20Now%20he%20wants%20his%20%245%20million.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22He%20proved%20the%20My%20Pillow%20Guy%20wrong%20about%20election%20fraud%20and%20won%20%245%20million.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6632857a10dfcda409657f97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20believe%20the%20world's%20out%20to%20get%20them%20because%20they%20think%20they%20are%20doing%20everything%20rationally%20but%20the%20world%20is%20not%20acting%20rationally%20in%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bob%20Zeidman.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20way%20Lindell%20is.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EJared%20Bartman%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEight%20months%20into%20Joe%20Biden's%20presidency%2C%20the%20MyPillow%20guy%2C%20Mike%20Lindell%2C%20staged%20an%20event%20in%20Sioux%20Falls%2C%20South%20Dakota%2C%20that%20he%20promised%20would%20return%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20The%20three-day%20Cyber%20Symposium%20revolved%20around%20a%20mysterious%20cache%20of%20computer%20data%20that%20Lindell%20had%20surreptitiously%20acquired.%20In%20his%20telling%2C%20the%20data%20proved%20that%20Chinese%20hackers%20had%20manipulated%20American%20voting%20machines%20into%20securing%20Biden's%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20election%20was%20stolen%2C%20and%20we're%20proving%20it%20right%20here%2C%20aren't%20we%3F%26quot%3B%20Lindell%20crowed%20to%20some%20200%20attendees%20on%20the%20first%20night%2C%20sweating%20through%20his%20suit.%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20is%20the%20rightful%20president%2C%20are%20you%20with%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20attendee%2C%20Bob%20Zeidman%2C%20who%20had%20voted%20for%20Trump%20twice%2C%20hoped%20this%20was%20true.%20A%20mild-mannered%2C%2064-year-old%20Republican%2C%20Zeidman%20chafed%20at%20the%20former%20president's%20demagoguery.%20But%20he's%20more%20repelled%20by%20the%20Democrats%2C%20whom%20he%20believes%20have%20%26quot%3Bgone%20so%20crazy%20with%20their%20wokeness%20and%20socialism.%26quot%3B%20As%20an%20authority%20in%20software%20forensics%20%E2%80%94%20the%20art%20of%20digital%20problem-solving%20%E2%80%94%20Zeidman%20has%20been%20an%20expert%20witness%20in%20more%20than%20260%20court%20cases%2C%20including%20the%202021%20Supreme%20Court%20battle%20between%20Oracle%20and%20Google%20and%20the%20fight%20between%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20the%20Winklevoss%20twins.%20He%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20evidence%20of%20vote%20rigging%20that%20Lindell%20claimed%20to%20have%20collected%2C%20and%20he%20was%20open%20to%20the%20possibility%20that%20a%20vast%20conspiracy%2C%20including%20Democrats%20using%20mail-in%20voting%20and%20ballot%20harvesting%20to%20fabricate%20votes%2C%20had%20stolen%20the%20election%20from%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20fraud%20in%20the%20election%20because%20there's%20fraud%20in%20every%20human%20endeavor%2C%26quot%3B%20Zeidman%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20fraud%3F%20I%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%20He%20had%20traveled%20to%20Sioux%20Falls%20intending%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindell%20had%20purchased%20his%20prized%20data%20for%20some%20%241.5%20million%20from%20a%20software%20developer%20named%20Dennis%20Montgomery.%20In%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20Montgomery%20had%20won%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20Pentagon%20contracts%20after%20he%20convinced%20the%20CIA%20that%20he%20had%20built%20software%20that%20could%20intercept%20terrorist%20messages%20concealed%20in%20Al%20Jazeera%20broadcasts.%20But%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20hoax%3A%20A%20top%20CIA%20official%20called%20Montgomery's%20software%20%26quot%3Bimaginary%20voodoo%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbullshit%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20one%20of%20Montgomery's%20own%20lawyers%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theregister.com%2F2009%2F12%2F24%2Fcia_montgomery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20called%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%26quot%3Bcon%20artist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20habitual%20liar%20engaged%20in%20fraud.%26quot%3B%20But%20none%20of%20that%20bothered%20Lindell.%20He%20praised%20Montgomery%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20smartest%20people%20that%20has%20ever%20walked%20this%20Earth.%26quot%3B%20And%20to%20prove%20his%20confidence%20in%20Montgomery's%20data%2C%20he%20announced%20a%20high-stakes%20wager%3A%20If%20anyone%20at%20the%20Cyber%20Symposium%20could%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20data%20did%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20show%20election%20meddling%2C%20he%20would%20award%20them%20%245%20million.%20He%20called%20it%20the%20Prove%20Mike%20Wrong%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBob%20Zeidman%20has%20many%20obsessions%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20is%20poker.%20He%20lives%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20where%20he%20competes%20in%20poker%20tournaments%20every%20week.%20He%20entered%20the%20Prove%20Mike%20Wrong%20challenge%20with%20low%20confidence%20he%20would%20win%20the%20exorbitant%20pot%2C%20estimating%20he%20had%20a%200.5%25%20chance%20of%20disproving%20Lindell's%20%26quot%3Bevidence.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20as%20he%20later%20wrote%20in%20a%20lengthy%20LinkedIn%20post%2C%20he%20would%20have%20a%20%26quot%3B100%25%20chance%20of%20being%20able%20to%20write%20about%20what%20would%20certainly%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20and%20important%20conferences%20in%20recent%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Zeidman%20analyzed%20the%20reams%20of%20data%20provided%20to%20him%20and%20the%20other%20cyber%20experts%20at%20the%20symposium%2C%20his%20confidence%20rose.%20When%20he%20converted%20the%20data%20into%20a%20Word%20document%2C%20he%20discovered%20it%20was%20filled%20with%20line%20after%20line%20of%20meaningless%20letters%20and%20numbers.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20somebody%20had%20typed%20in%20what%20they%20imagined%20computer%20code%20might%20look%20like.%20%26quot%3BI%20confirmed%20that%20it%20was%20perfectly%20formatted%2C%20legitimate%20gibberish%2C%26quot%3B%20Zeidman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20it%20was%20a%20real%20Word%20document%20filled%20with%20gibberish%2C%20not%20a%20document%20that%20Word%20didn't%20understand.%26quot%3B%20Even%20more%20suspiciously%2C%20the%20data%20files%20were%20time-stamped%20to%20just%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20symposium%2C%20meaning%20they%20were%20likely%20created%20for%20the%20event%2C%20not%20collected%20from%20errant%20voting%20machines.%20The%20numbers%20purporting%20to%20demonstrate%20election%20fraud%2C%20Zeidman%20concluded%2C%20were%20themselves%20a%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20second%20day%2C%20Zeidman%20was%20certain%20he%20had%20disproved%20Lindell's%20claims.%20He%20filed%20a%20damning%20report%20and%20registered%20a%20copy%20online%20with%20the%20US%20Copyright%20Office%20as%20proof%20he%20had%20written%20it%20by%20the%20contest%20deadline.%20Then%20he%20called%20his%20wife%20from%20the%20hotel%20parking%20lot.%20%26quot%3BAll%20I%20want%20to%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20her%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20that%20you%20should%20start%20thinking%20about%20how%20you%20want%20to%20spend%20%245%20million.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20home%20to%20Vegas%2C%20Zeidman%20waited%20to%20hear%20from%20Lindell's%20people%20about%20the%20award.%20Though%20he%20is%20already%20a%20multimillionaire%2C%20with%20several%20patents%20and%20businesses%20to%20his%20name%2C%20%245%20million%20remained%20an%20exciting%20prospect.%20Antsy%20with%20nervous%20energy%2C%20he%20upped%20his%20poker%20playing.%20But%20as%20a%20Trump%20backer%2C%20he%20was%20puzzled%20by%20the%20obvious%20fraudulence%20of%20the%20data%2C%20which%20he%20laid%20out%20in%20his%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fi-uncovered-fraud-mike-lindells-cyber-symposium-election-bob-zeidman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%20post%3A%20%26quot%3BWas%20someone%20sabotaging%20Mike's%20data%3F%20Or%20had%20Mike%20been%20bamboozled%3F%20Or%20was%20Mike%20the%20bamboozler%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20weeks%20later%2C%20Lindell's%20team%20finally%20got%20back%20to%20Zeidman%3A%20They%20were%20refusing%20to%20pay%20up.%20Zeidman%2C%20they%20argued%2C%20had%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20challenge%2C%20which%20stipulated%20that%20a%20winner%20must%20prove%20%26quot%3Bto%20100%25%20certainty%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20data%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Brelated%20to%20the%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUndeterred%2C%20Zeidman%20sued%20one%20of%20Trump's%20most%20vociferous%20advocates%20for%20contract%20violation.%20In%20February%2C%20after%20days%20of%20deliberation%2C%20an%20arbitration%20proceeding%20in%20Minnesota%20sided%20with%20Zeidman.%20He%20had%20indeed%20Proven%20Mike%20Wrong%2C%20and%20now%20Mike%20must%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20ruling%2C%20I%20arrived%20in%20Vegas%20to%20meet%20Zeidman.%20His%20handsome%20home%20sits%20in%20a%20gated%20community%20in%20Sumerlin%2C%20a%20residential%20area%20in%20the%20high%20desert.%20A%20%26quot%3BStand%20With%20Israel%26quot%3B%20sign%20adorned%20his%20front%20yard.%20He%20and%20his%20artist%20wife%2C%20Carrie%2C%20collect%20modern%20art%2C%20which%20crowded%20the%20walls%20of%20their%20living%20room.%20Out%20back%20was%20a%20large%20pool.%20Recently%2C%20after%20Zeidman%20started%20swimming%20regularly%2C%20he%20became%20frustrated%20with%20trying%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20his%20laps%2C%20so%20he%20invented%20a%20counting%20instrument%20to%20do%20it%20for%20him.%20A%20newly%20patented%20prototype%20sat%20on%20the%20kitchen%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20interested%20in%20what%20impact%2C%20if%20any%2C%20Zeidman's%20experience%20with%20Lindell%20had%20made%20on%20his%20politics.%20Lindell%2C%20for%20all%20his%20cartoonish%20bombast%2C%20has%20clearly%20been%20following%20a%20path%20of%20election%20denial%20forged%20by%20Trump.%20It%20is%20Trump%2C%20after%20all%2C%20who%20has%20made%20his%20case%20for%20voter%20fraud%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20his%20reelection%20campaign.%20The%20fabrications%20have%20been%20wildly%20successful%20at%20firing%20up%20his%20base%3A%20Recent%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Felections%2F2024%2F01%2F04%2Fjan-6-trump-voters-believe-fraud-2024%2F72072407007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20polling%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20Trump's%20supporters%20believe%20that%20the%202020%20election%20was%20%26quot%3Bstolen%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZeidman%2C%20though%20sympathetic%2C%20is%20not%20fully%20on%20board.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Lindell%20is%20doing%20is%20hurting%20America%20and%20hurting%20Republicans%2C%20because%20it's%20dividing%20us%20and%20it's%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI've%20had%20a%20few%20other%20Republicans%20say%20to%20me%2C%20'OK%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20broadcast%20this.'%20And%20I%20say%2C%20'No%2C%20it's%20the%20truth.%20The%20truth%20has%20to%20be%20out%20there.%20We%20allegedly%20stand%20for%20the%20truth%2C%20OK%3F%20Not%20the%20relative%20truth%2C%20but%20the%20absolute%20truth.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Lidell%2C%20deep%20in%20his%20zany%20campaign%20of%20misinformation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663286430dfb1341e9015ca7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Lindell%20is%20doing%20is%20hurting%20America%20and%20hurting%20Republicans%2C%20because%20it's%20dividing%20us%20and%20it's%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zeidman.%3Cp%3EJared%20Bartman%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZeidman%20requires%20constant%20stimulation.%20During%20meetings%2C%20he%20makes%20sure%20to%20sit%20by%20a%20door%20in%20case%20boredom%20forces%20him%20to%20flee.%20Whenever%20he's%20idle%2C%20he%20becomes%20%26quot%3Bterribly%20depressed.%26quot%3B%20To%20keep%20busy%2C%20he%20invents%20gizmos%20and%20software.%20He%20pens%20satirical%20political%20novels%20and%20computer-science%20textbooks%20and%20conservative%20op-eds%20on%20his%20Substack%20or%20for%20publications%20like%20the%20Cleveland%20Jewish%20News.%20He%20adores%20movies%2C%20though%20plot%20holes%20ruffle%20him.%20His%20favorite%20film%20is%20%26quot%3BMemento%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20%26quot%3Bit%20all%20connects%20together.%26quot%3B%20He%20speaks%20regularly%20at%20engineering%20conferences%20and%20attends%20political%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20young%20adulthood%2C%20Zeidman%20has%20%26quot%3Bleaned%20conservative.%26quot%3B%20But%20it%20was%20not%20until%20the%20presidency%20of%20George%20W.%20Bush%20that%20he%20started%20going%20to%20political%20events%20and%20closely%20following%20party%20politics.%20He%20describes%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Brare%20species%26quot%3B%3A%20a%20Republican%20Jew.%20American%20support%20for%20Israel%20is%20one%20of%20his%20chief%20concerns.%20He%20remains%20a%20great%20fan%20of%20Bush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20always%20found%20Trump%20distasteful%3A%20%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20really%20nasty%20guy.%26quot%3B%20Yet%20he%20understands%20Trump's%20appeal%20as%20a%20totem%20of%20conservative%20grievance%2C%20much%20of%20which%20he%20shares%3A%20left-wing%20media%20bias%2C%20high%20taxes%2C%20political%20correctness.%20He%20pinpoints%20the%20genesis%20of%20Trump's%20rise%20to%20Mitt%20Romney's%20loss%20to%20Barack%20Obama%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Democratic%20Party%20attacked%20Romney%20so%20strongly%20on%20moral%20issues%20when%20this%20man%20was%20an%20outstanding%20moral%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20pissed%20off%20so%20many%20people%20that%20they%20said%2C%20'OK%2C%20whoever%20we%20put%20in%20office%20is%20going%20to%20be%20trashed%2C%20so%20let's%20find%20a%20guy%20who%20trashes%20back.'%20And%20that%20was%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20guy%20who%20trashes%20back%20is%20Mike%20Lindell.%20After%20numerous%20failed%20ventures%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bar%2C%20a%20food%20truck%2C%20a%20carpet-cleaning%20business%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Minnesota%20native%20found%20wild%20success%20with%20his%20company%20MyPillow%2C%20which%20he%20claims%20hit%20revenues%20of%20%24300%20million%20in%202018.%20His%20zany%20infomercials%2C%20signature%20mustache%2C%20and%20Midwestern%20whimsy%20became%20a%20TV%20staple%20across%20the%20country.%20(Zeidman%20himself%20is%20a%20happy%20customer%3B%20he%20enjoys%20the%20pillow's%20%26quot%3Bslumber-inducing%20qualities.%26quot%3B)%20Even%20more%20impressive%2C%20Lindell%20prevailed%20after%20overcoming%20a%20severe%20crack%20addiction%2C%20as%20recounted%20in%20his%20memoir%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Are%20the%20Odds%3F%20From%20Crack%20Addict%20to%20CEO%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20In%20recovery%2C%20he%20became%20a%20committed%20evangelical%20Christian.%20Trump%2C%20he%20believes%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bchosen%20by%20God%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20transactional%20way%2C%20Trump%20has%20returned%20the%20compliment.%20Following%20his%20victory%20in%202016%2C%20he%20invited%20Lindell%20to%20meet%20him%20in%20Trump%20Tower.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20two%20have%20appeared%20together%20at%20the%20White%20House%20and%20at%20campaign%20events.%20In%20March%2C%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20Trump%20praised%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20great%2C%20legendary%20Mike%20Lindell.%26quot%3B%20Lara%20Trump%2C%20Trump's%20daughter-in-law%20and%20the%20new%20cochair%20of%20the%20Republican%20National%20Committee%2C%20hawks%20MyPillow%20products%20on%20her%20podcast%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Right%20View.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20amount%20of%20praise%20can%20make%20up%20for%20the%20losses%20Lindell%2C%20now%2062%2C%20has%20endured%20for%20his%20favorite%20president.%20In%20a%20defamation%20suit%20brought%20by%20the%20voting-machine%20firm%20Dominion%20Voting%20Systems%2C%20Lindell%20and%20MyPillow%20were%20found%20liable%20for%20a%20staggering%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20damages%2C%20which%20far%20exceeds%20his%20net%20worth.%20Lindell's%20lawyers%20have%20since%20quit%2C%20because%2C%20they%20say%2C%20he%20has%20not%20paid%20them.%20Another%20defamation%20case%20brought%20by%20the%20voting-machine%20firm%20Smartmatic%20is%20ongoing.%20Recently%2C%20Lindell%20claimed%20he%20had%20just%20%2410%2C000%20left%20to%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20spoke%20to%20Lindell%2C%20he%20balked%20when%20I%20asked%20if%20he%20regrets%20his%20decision%20to%20wage%20a%20one-man%20crusade%20against%20electronic%20voting%20machines.%20%26quot%3BDo%20I%20regret%20spending%20%2440%20million%20trying%20to%20save%20our%20country%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20these%20computers%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20boomed.%20%26quot%3BNo!%26quot%3B%20He%20repeatedly%20disparaged%20Zeidman%20as%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20cyber%20expert%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20patently%20untrue.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20all%20contrived%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Zeidman's%20report.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20their%20plan%20is%2C%20whoever%20he's%20working%20with%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20disgusting%20what%20he's%20trying%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Looking%20triumphant%20as%20the%20sky%20rains%20flaming%20pillows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663286d810dfcda4096580d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BDo%20I%20regret%20spending%20%2440%20million%20trying%20to%20save%20our%20country%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20these%20computers%3F%26quot%3B%20Lindell%20boomed.%20%26quot%3BNo!%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EJared%20Bartman%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20deposition%20in%20the%20arbitration%20proceedings%20over%20his%20refusal%20to%20pay%20Zeidman%2C%20Lindell%20was%20a%20tornado%20of%20evasion%20and%20contradiction.%20He%20claimed%2C%20confusingly%2C%20that%20the%2023%20gigabytes%20of%20data%20he%20bragged%20about%20at%20the%20Cyber%20Symposium%20were%20not%20actually%20intended%20to%20%3Cem%3Eprove%3C%2Fem%3E%20election%20interference%3B%20they%20were%20only%20%26quot%3Brelated%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20some%20unspecified%20fashion%2C%20to%20the%202020%20election.%20Moreover%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20could%20not%20make%20public%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20data%20trove%20that%20%3Cem%3Edo%20%3C%2Fem%3Eprove%20election%20interference%20for%20reasons%20of%20%26quot%3Bnational%20security.%26quot%3B%20With%20a%20Trumpian%20redirect%2C%20Lindell%20assured%20Zeidman's%20lawyer%2C%20Brian%20Glasser%2C%20that%20he%20had%20%3Cem%3Efar%20%3C%2Fem%3Emore%20shocking%20evidence%20in%20hand%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20was%20being%20blocked%20from%20releasing%20it%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20gag%20order%26quot%3B%20issued%20by%20a%20judge%20in%20Nevada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20same%20data%20we're%20talking%20about%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20the%20Cyber%20Symposium%3F%26quot%3B%20Glasser%20pressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindell%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20goes%20a%20lot%20deeper%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%20The%20explosive%20evidence%2C%20he%20implied%2C%20would%20prove%20that%20Zeidman%20was%20wrong%3A%20The%20election%20%3Cem%3Ewas%20%3C%2Fem%3Estolen.%20%26quot%3BDennis%20Montgomery%20has%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20just%20that%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindell%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Zeidman's%20lawyers%20tracked%20down%20the%20case%20Lindell%20was%20referring%20to.%20Nobody%2C%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20was%20preventing%20Lindell%20from%20releasing%20any%20data.%20The%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bgag%20order%26quot%3B%20was%20issued%20in%202007%20as%20part%20of%20a%20contract%20dispute%20between%20Montgomery%20and%20eTreppid%20Technologies%20(the%20company%20Montgomery%20ran%20that%20had%20defrauded%20the%20government)%2C%20relating%20to%20government%20contracts%20and%20related%20%26quot%3Btrade%20secrets.%26quot%3B%20Lindell%20had%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20remove%20the%20order%2C%20arguing%20that%20he%20somehow%20needed%20to%20release%20the%20data%20to%20defend%20himself%20in%20his%20unrelated%20defamation%20cases.%20The%20court%20denied%20his%20request%2C%20saying%20the%20order%20didn't%20apply%20to%20him.%20%26quot%3BLindell%20provides%20nothing%20more%20than%20speculation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20he%20will%20somehow%20be%20precluded%20from%20presenting%20this%20information%20because%20of%20the%20protective%20order%20in%20this%20litigation.%26quot%3B%20In%20December%202022%2C%20Lindell%20said%20he%20would%20release%20the%20data%20within%2060%20days.%20He%20never%20did%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZeidman%20pities%20Lindell%20for%20what%20he%20sees%20as%20his%20sincere%20conspiratorial%20convictions.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20believe%20the%20world's%20out%20to%20get%20them%20because%20they%20think%20they%20are%20doing%20everything%20rationally%20but%20the%20world%20is%20not%20acting%20rationally%20in%20response%2C%20when%20really%20it's%20the%20other%20way%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20the%20way%20Lindell%20is.%20He's%20angry%20because%20he%20doesn't%20understand%20why%20people%20don't%20believe%20him.%20In%20his%20mind%2C%20people%20irrationally%20hate%20him%20for%20telling%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Vegas%2C%20Zeidman%20drove%20me%20to%20The%20Venetian%20for%20lunch%2C%20where%20he%20had%20a%20poker%20tournament%20later%20that%20afternoon.%20On%20the%20way%2C%20he%20gestured%20toward%20the%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%2C%20towering%20over%20Sin%20City%20like%20a%20giant%20golden%20Zippo.%20Long%20before%20Trump%20ran%20for%20office%2C%20Zeidman%20had%20followed%20his%20business%20ventures%20with%20bewilderment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20would%20run%20his%20businesses%20into%20the%20ground%20yet%20somehow%20make%20a%20windfall%20profit%20and%20get%20investors%20to%20invest%20in%20his%20next%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20thinking%2C%20don't%20they%20look%20at%20the%20records%20and%20see%20that%20people%20have%20gotten%20burned%20by%20him%3F%20Why%20would%20they%20invest%20in%20his%20next%20project%3F%20How%20can%20he%20talk%20them%20into%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20for%20all%20his%20problems%20with%20Trump%2C%20Zeidman%20sees%20the%20incumbent%20as%20no%20less%20deceitful.%20%26quot%3BBiden%20is%20the%20Democrats'%20version%20of%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20liar.%20He's%20uncouth.%20He%20says%20stupid%20things%20and%20insults%20people.%26quot%3B%20This%20equivalency%20struck%20me%20as%20an%20exaggeration%20of%20Lindellian%20proportions.%20But%20Zeidman%20stood%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20likelihood%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he'll%20be%20voting%20for%20Trump%20come%20November.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20vote%20for%20Trump%20because%20he's%20scary%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20vote%20for%20Biden%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20the%20decision%20is%3A%20Biden's%20policies%20have%20made%20America%20weaker%20and%20Trump's%20policies%20made%20it%20stronger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20way%20to%20The%20Venetian%2C%20Zeidman%20stopped%20by%20his%20bank%20to%20retrieve%20cash%20for%20the%20tournament%20buy-in%20(%26quot%3BThis%20one%20is%20%24800%2C%20which%20is%20relatively%20cheap%26quot%3B).%20He%20was%20already%20strategizing.%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20to%20win%20a%20poker%20tournament%20is%20to%20survive%20until%20later%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20how%20many%20chips%20you%20have%2C%20because%20later%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%20blinds%20%E2%80%94%20the%20minimum%20bets%20%E2%80%94%20are%20so%20big%20that%20one%20hand%20can%20flip%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20casino%2C%20hundreds%20of%20players%20sat%20silently%20at%20small%20tables%20in%20a%20windowless%20poker%20room.%20The%20exchange%20of%20chips%20crackled%20through%20the%20stale%20air%20like%20the%20snapping%20shrimp%20of%20coral%20reefs.%20Zeidman%20competed%20until%202%20a.m.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20he%20came%20in%2010th%20out%20of%20330%20players%2C%20earning%20a%20%241%2C000%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20big%20money%20is%20really%20at%20the%20top.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unlikely%20that%20Zeidman%20will%20see%20his%20%245%20million%20from%20Lindell.%20Lindell%20is%20appealing%20the%20binding%20arbitration%20ruling%20in%20federal%20court.%20In%20March%2C%20his%20lawyers%20subpoenaed%20records%20of%20Lindell's%20financial%20assets%2C%20but%20Lindell's%20new%20lawyer%20has%20been%20slow%20to%20respond.%20Zeidman%20suspects%20that%20Lindell%20will%20try%20to%20transfer%20his%20assets%20out%20of%20his%20company%2C%20Lindell%20Management%2C%20which%2C%20legally%20speaking%2C%20is%20the%20offending%20party%20in%20their%20dispute.%20When%20we%20spoke%2C%20Lindell%20wanted%20to%20make%20that%20distinction%20clear.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20against%20Lindell%20Management%2C%20a%20management%20company%20that%20managed%20that%20event%20and%20other%20events.%20You%20know%20that%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Zeidman%20is%20glad%20to%20have%20Proven%20Mike%20Wrong.%20He%20had%20played%20his%20part%20in%20disseminating%20an%20important%20truth.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20Republicans%20don't%20believe%20Lindell%20now%2C%20and%20maybe%20I%20had%20a%20part%20in%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20Then%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20still%20believe%20the%20election%20was%20stolen%20through%20ballot%20harvesting%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20allowing%20political%20campaigns%20to%20collect%20and%20submit%20absentee%20ballots%20on%20behalf%20of%20voters%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Band%20things%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20the%20obvious%20follow-up%3A%20Does%20Zeidman%20believe%20this%20improbable%20claim%2C%20which%20numerous%20studies%2C%20scholars%2C%20legislatures%2C%20and%20judges%20have%20thoroughly%20disproven%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20isn't%20sure.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20idea%20if%20things%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20we%20didn't%20have%20all%20the%20ballot%20harvesting%20and%20mail-in%20ballots%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20inveterate%20engineer%2C%20Zeidman%20avoids%20too%20much%20speculation.%20He%20prefers%20the%20hard%20certainty%20of%20numbers%3A%20differentiating%20complex%20code%2C%20investigating%20algorithms%2C%20analyzing%20technical%20patents.%20These%20are%20the%20skills%20he%20used%20to%20debunk%20Lindell's%20data.%20What%20Zeidman%3Cem%3E%20is%3C%2Fem%3E%20sure%20about%2C%20and%20what%20worries%20him%20most%2C%20isn't%20election%20interference.%20It%20is%20the%20perilous%20state%20of%20the%20country%20that%20those%20elections%2C%20as%20he%20sees%20it%2C%20have%20produced%3A%20woke%20lunacy%2C%20border%20instability%2C%20unrestrained%20crime%2C%20and%20rising%20antisemitism.%20Trump%2C%20he%20concedes%2C%20is%20no%20paragon%20of%20order.%20But%20if%20the%20former%20president%20can%20mend%20all%20of%20that%2C%20then%20perhaps%20he%20is%20the%20only%20logical%20choice.%20A%20guy%20like%20Bob%20Zeidman%20looks%20at%20America%20and%20wonders%3A%20%3Cem%3EWhere%20did%20all%20the%20rational%20people%20go%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBrent%C2%A0Crane%C2%A0is%20a%20reporter%20based%20in%20San%20Diego.%20His%20work%20can%20be%20found%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brent-crane.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ewww.brent-crane.com%3C%2Fu%