202014%20and%20it%20created%20many%20problems%20for%20the%20country%2C%20Jaishankar%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20suggested%20that%20lack%20of%20focus%20in%20the%20past%20to%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20upward%20trajectory%20in%20India-China%20trade%20notwithstanding%20New%20Delhi's%20position%20that%20normalisation%20of%20ties%20with%20Beijing%20is%20dependent%20on%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20eastern%20Ladakh%20border%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20confident.%20I%20am%20clear%20that%20international%20politics%2C%20international%20relations%20are%20competitive.%20I%20have%20a%20neighbour%20like%20China.%20I%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20compete%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20my%20complaining%2C%20China%20is%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20doing%20things.%20If%20I%20do%20not%20build%20up%20my%20strength%20at%20home%2C%20our%20foreign%20policy%20will%20be%20as%20good%20as%20our%20domestic%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20function%20of%20our%20domestic%20policy%20that%20if%20I%20can%20actually%20build%20up%20my%20economy%2C%20if%20I%20can%20build%20up%20my%20manufacturing%2C%20if%20I%20can%20create%20the%20kind%20of%20capabilities%20which%20today%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20do%2C%20I%20think%20you%20are%20going%20to%20find%20foreign%20policy%20has%20much%20more%20resources%20and%20much%20more%20tool%20in%20its%20toolkit%20to%20actually%20influence%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20response%20came%20when%20asked%20why%20India's%20bilateral%20trade%20volume%20with%20China%20is%20going%20up%20when%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20insisting%20that%20ties%20cannot%20be%20normal%20if%20the%20border%20situation%20is%20abnormal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20suggested%20that%20such%20a%20scenario%20has%20arisen%20as%20adequate%20attention%20to%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20was%20not%20given%20before%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20militaries%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20standoff%20since%20May%202020%20and%20a%20full%20resolution%20of%20the%20border%20row%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20achieved%20though%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20disengaged%20from%20a%20number%20of%20friction%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20common%20sense%20that%20if%20there%20is%20no%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20border%2C%20how%20can%20you%20have%20a%20normal%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20all%20if%20somebody%20is%20at%20your%20front%20door%20in%20an%20unfriendly%20manner%2C%20you%20are%20not%20going%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20act%20as%20though%20everything%20is%20normal.%20That%20to%20me%20is%20a%20straightforward%20proposition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20consistently%20maintaining%20that%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20along%20the%20LAC%20were%20key%20for%20normalisation%20of%20overall%20ties.%20However%2C%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20steadily%20expanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20bilateral%20trade%20between%20India%20and%20China%20recorded%20significant%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202015%20to%202022%2C%20India-China%20bilateral%20trade%20grew%20by%2090.14%20per%20cent%2C%20an%20average%20yearly%20growth%20of%2012.87%20per%20cent.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20overall%20trade%20with%20China%20increased%20by%208.47%20per%20cent%20year%20on%20year%20to%20reach%20USD%20136.26%20billion%2C%20crossing%20the%20USD%20100%20billion%20mark%20for%20a%20second%20time%20in%20a%20row%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20trade%20deficit%20came%20at%20USD%20101.28%20billion%20as%20India's%20imports%20from%20China%20witnessed%20major%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20making%20efforts%20to%20expand%20manufacturing%20in%20a%20number%20of%20critical%20areas%20as%20part%20of%20an%20aim%20to%20de-risking%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20trade%2C%20what%20has%20happened%20is%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20actually%20neglected%20manufacturing%20in%20this%20country.%20That%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20we%20did%20not%20give%20the%20kind%20of%20support%20to%20our%20manufacturers%2C%20especially%20our%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%20listed%20various%20initiatives%20rolled%20out%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20including%20the%20'Make%20in%20India'%20and%20'Production%20Linked%20Incentive'%20(PLI)%20schemes%2C%20to%20enhance%20domestic%20manufacturing%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%20when%20Make%20in%20India%20was%20started%2C%20you%20have%20people%20who%20even%20laughed%20at%20it.%20Even%20now%20there%20are%20people%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20believe%20that%20we%20are%20incapable%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20this%20country%20and%20there%20are%20some%20economists%20who%20also%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20our%20manufacturing%20fell%20behind%2C%20I%20think%2C%20has%20created%20many%20of%20the%20problems%20that%20today%20we%20are%20experiencing%20today.%20You%20cannot%20get%20an%20immediate%20fix%20but%20what%20you%20can%20do%2C%20which%20we%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20do%2C%20is%20actually%20to%20boost%20manufacturing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20said%20the%20government%20is%20rapidly%20modernising%20infrastructure%20and%20making%20it%20as%20efficient%20as%20possible%20as%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20efficient%20infrastructure%2C%20you%20are%20not%20going%20to%20get%20competitive%20manufacturing.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20how%20the%20environment%20was%20used%20as%20an%20argument%20to%20make%20business%20very%20difficult%20in%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20overall%20development%20trajectory%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20he%20was%20more%20optimistic%20than%20ever%20about%20India's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20much%20more%20optimistic%20for%20our%20country%20than%20I%20have%20been%20all%20my%20life%20--%20part%20of%20it%20is%20because%20I%20also%20see%20the%20abilities%20and%20talent%20of%20younger%20people%3B%20what%20they%20can%20do%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20achievements%20they%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20PTI%20MPB%20ANB%20DV%20DV%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715505180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fce5oq5io_jaishankar_625x300_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneighbour-like-china-have-to-learn-to-compete-s-jaishankar-on-indias-manufacturing-5644842%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boosting%20India's%20domestic%20manufacturing%20and%20the%20overall%20economy%20will%20provide%20much%20more%20resources%20in%20its%20foreign%20policy%20toolkit%20to%20expand%20the%20country's%20influence%20globally%20and%20compete%20with%20China%20on%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneighbour-like-china-have-to-learn-to-compete-s-jaishankar-on-indias-manufacturing-5644842%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneighbour-like-china-have-to-learn-to-compete-s-jaishankar-on-indias-manufacturing-5644842%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneighbour-like-china-have-to-learn-to-compete-s-jaishankar-on-indias-manufacturing-5644842%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20a%2065%25%20stock%20market%20crash%20to%20an%20imminent%20recession%2C%20here's%20a%20roundup%20of%20recent%20high-profile%20bear%20forecasts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222518%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20bears%20appear%20to%20converse%20with%20each%20other%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e542a9686a6f37bfe98f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221258%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26amp%3BquotBear%20Jokes%26quot%3B%20by%20Sidra%20Monreal%20Burshteyn.%3Cp%3ESidra%20Monreal%20Burshteyn%2FComedy%20Wildlife%20Awards%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDespite%20a%20stock%20market%20that's%20less%20than%201%25%20away%20from%20record%20highs%2C%20bearish%20forecasts%20are%20out%20in%20full%20force.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20economists%20and%20portfolio%20managers%20are%20warnings%20of%20everything%20from%20an%20imminent%20recession%20to%20the%20potential%20for%20a%2065%25%20stock-market%20crash.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutlined%20below%20are%20assorted%20high-profile%20bear%20forecasts%20from%20across%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20stock%20market%20less%20than%201%25%20away%20from%20a%20record%20high%2C%20top%20forecasters%20who%20have%20consistently%20leaned%20bearish%20can't%20shake%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20painful%20decline%20is%20imminent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20warn%20of%20an%20imminent%20recession%20following%20a%20weaker-than-expected%20April%20jobs%20report%20that%20coincided%20with%20a%20jump%20in%20weekly%20jobless%20claims%2C%20while%20others%20suggest%20a%20stock%20market%20crash%20similar%20to%201929%20is%20about%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20forecasts%20have%20fallen%20flat%20on%20their%20face%20so%20far%2C%20they're%20still%20worth%20monitoring%20as%20a%20way%20for%20investors%20to%20poke%20potential%20holes%20in%20the%20consistently%20bullish%20narrative%20that%20the%20economy%2C%20corporate%20profits%2C%20and%20stock%20market%20are%20doing%20just%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20roundup%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20bearish%20forecasts%20coming%20from%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EGary%20Shilling%3A%20Recession%20by%20year-end%20means%2030%25%20stock%20market%20plunge%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20veteran%20Gary%20Shilling%20told%20Business%20Insider%20this%20week%20that%20he%20expects%20a%20recession%20to%20materialize%20in%20the%20US%20economy%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20as%20the%20labor%20market%20shows%20signs%20of%20weakening.%20And%20a%20weakening%20in%20the%20labor%20market%20will%20crush%20investor%20confidence%20and%20send%20the%20stock%20market%20falling%20by%20as%20much%20as%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20look%20at%20all%20the%20kind%20of%20speculation%20that%20we've%20had%20out%20there%2C%20it's%20indicative%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20overconfidence%2C%20and%20that%20usually%20gets%20corrected%20and%20corrected%20violently%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-recession-outlook-layoffs-job-market-gary-shilling-2024-5%5C%22%3EShilling%20told%20BI's%20Jennifer%20Sor.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20the%20safe%20bet%20is%20for%20a%20recession%20starting%20later%20this%20year%20if%20we're%20not%20already%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShilling%20is%20known%20for%20correctly%20identifying%20the%20US%20housing%20bubble%20in%20the%20mid-2000's%2C%20though%20most%20of%20his%20consistently%20bearish%20views%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20have%20yet%20to%20pan%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EJohn%20Hussman%3A%20A%2065%25%20stock-market%20crash%20wouldn't%20be%20surprising%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Hussman%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Hussman%20Investment%20Trust%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-crash-outlook-1929-bear-market-overvalued-john-hussman-2024-5%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20bearish%20warning%20on%20stocks%20this%20past%20week%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20arguing%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20trading%20at%20similar%20extremes%20seen%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%201929%20Great%20Depression%20as%20the%20fear-of-missing-out%20takes%20over%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStatistically%2C%20the%20current%20set%20of%20market%20conditions%20looks%20more%20'like'%20a%20major%20bull%20market%20peak%20than%20any%20other%20point%20in%20the%20past%20century%2C%20with%20the%20possible%20exception%20of%20the%201929%20peak%2C%26quot%3B%20Hussman%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20valuations%2C%20unfavorable%20market%20internals%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20other%20factors%26quot%3B%20give%20him%20comfort%20in%20having%20a%20bearish%20outlook%20on%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20surprised%20if%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20crashed%2065%25%2C%20which%20would%20erase%20a%20decade%20of%20stock%20market%20gains%20and%20put%20the%20index%20at%20about%201%2C800%2C%20or%20where%20it%20traded%20at%20back%20in%20February%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20is%20famous%20for%20successfully%20warnings%20about%20the%202000%20dot-com%20bubble%20and%20the%202008%20housing%20market%20crash%2C%20though%20his%20consistently%20bearish%20predictions%20since%20then%20have%20yet%20to%20fully%20materialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBCA%20Research%3A%20A%20recession%20in%20early%202025%20will%20cause%2030%25%20stock%20market%20decline%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBCA%20strategist%20Roukaya%20Ibrahim%20warned%20that%20a%2030%25%20correction%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20could%20be%20sparked%20by%20a%20recession%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIbrahim%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crass-recession-in-2025-tumble-stocks-by-30-2024-5%5C%22%3Etold%20Bloomberg%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20elevated%20stock%20valuations%20and%20decelerating%20growth%20would%20send%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20back%20down%20to%203%2C600%2C%20which%20is%20around%20where%20the%20index%20bottomed%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIbrahim%20pointed%20to%20the%20April%20employment%20report%2C%20which%20saw%20175%2C000%20jobs%20added%20to%20the%20economy%2C%20revealed%20lower%20job%20openings%2C%20hires%2C%20and%20quit%20rates%2C%20all%20of%20which%20signal%20a%20shifting%20narrative%20toward%20economic%20downside%2C%20not%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEventually%2C%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20is%20going%20to%20take%20higher%20and%20that's%20going%20to%20lead%20to%20concerns%20about%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Ibrahim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDavid%20Rosenberg%3A%20Signs%20are%20growing%20of%20a%20potential%20hard-landing%20in%20the%20economy%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-outlook-us-economy-job-market-hard-landing-gdp-growth-2024-5%5C%22%3EUS%20might%20be%20%26quot%3Bsleepwalking%26quot%3B%20into%20a%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20labor%20market%20shows%20signs%20of%20weakening%2C%20according%20to%20top%20economist%20David%20Rosenberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20constantly%20asked%20when%20we're%20planning%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20towel%20on%20our%20recession%20call%2C%20but%20perhaps%20it's%20time%20folks%20started%20asking%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20street%20is%20going%20to%20pick%20their%20towels%20back%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said%20in%20a%20note%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20a%20downshift%20in%20the%20data%20flow%20that%20are%20starting%20to%20indicate%20that%20the%20downturn%20in%20the%20economy%20may%20not%20be%20as%20far%20away%20as%20many%20believe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20said%20the%20Sahm%20Rule%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20flashing%20a%20recessionary%20warning%20after%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20ticked%20higher%20to%203.9%25%20in%20April%2C%20and%20that%20manufacturing%20activity%20contracted%20for%20the%2017th%20month%20out%20of%20the%20last%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20get%20complacent.%20The%20labor%20market%20is%20cracking%2C%20a%20slowdown%20in%20services%20activity%20is%20dragging%20on%20real-time%20growth%2C%20and%20forward%20looking%20financial%20signals%20still%20point%20to%20a%20coming%20slowdown%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%20famously%20predicted%20the%202008%20recession%2C%20but%20his%20consistently%20bearish%20economic%20outlooks%20since%20then%20have%20largely%20fallen%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20counterpoint%3A%20A%20bullish%20take%20to%20balance%20out%20the%20doomsayers%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20investment%20strategist%20who%20has%20been%20consistently%20bullish%2C%20and%20therefore%20right%2C%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20is%20market%20veteran%20Ed%20Yardeni.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYardeni%20said%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20economic%20doomsayers%20are%20likely%20once%20again%20too%20early%20in%20their%20recession%20predictions%20following%20the%20weaker-than-expected%20April%20jobs%20report%20and%20weekly%20initial%20jobless%20claims%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20widely%20anticipated%20recession%20of%20all%20times%20is%20turning%20into%20the%20longest%20widely%20anticipated%20recession%20of%20all%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20market%20veteran%20Ed%20Yardeni%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20day%2C%20the%20diehard%20hard-landers%20will%20be%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20day%20probably%20won't%20come%20anytime%20soon%2C%20according%20to%20Yardeni%2C%20as%20corporate%20profit%20estimates%20continue%20to%20hit%20record%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForward%20earnings%20rose%20to%20a%20record%20high%20during%20April%2C%20consistent%20with%20a%20solid%20labor%20market.%20So%20we%20don't%20buy%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20latest%20jobless%20claims%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20significant%20downturn%20in%20the%20labor%20market%20and%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Yardeni%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-predictions-recession-soon-inflation-corporate-profits-decline-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715505121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5448f27898f532d65c9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-crash-predictions-recession-soon-inflation-corporate-profits-decline-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20there's%20been%20a%20slew%20of%20bearish%20predictions%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20positive%20scenarios%20for%20the%20economy%20and%20markets%20remain.%20Choose%20your%20adventure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-crash-predictions-recession-soon-inflation-corporate-profits-decline-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dia%20Mirza%20talks%20about%20motherhood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715505106000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110053262%2Cimgsize-27116.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdia-mirza-talks-about-motherhood-says-i-was-sure-i-wanted-to-be-a-parent%2Farticleshow%2F110053203.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110053203.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C