.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-apple-stock-sales-dietrich-market-crash-recession-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20wargame%20simulated%20a%202nd%20Trump%20presidency.%20It%20concluded%20NATO%20would%20collapse.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20soldiers%20participated%20in%20the%20DEFENDER%2024%20exercise%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20intended%20to%20strengthen%20the%20NATO%20alliance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5dc1f27898f532d66a37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20soldiers%20participated%20in%20the%20DEFENDER%2024%20exercise%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20intended%20to%20strengthen%20the%20NATO%20alliance.%3Cp%3ELukas%20Kabon%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20has%20threatened%20to%20quit%20NATO.%20A%20wargame%20examined%20the%20possible%20ramifications.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20player%20abandoned%20Ukraine%20and%20ceased%20NATO%20participation%2C%20triggering%20crisis%20in%20Europe.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20game's%20designer%20says%20it%20showed%20Trump%C2%A0%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20need%20to%20leave%20NATO%20to%20ruin%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Donald%20Trump%20wins%20a%20second%20term%20in%20the%20White%20House%20in%20November%2C%20NATO%20may%20fall%20apart%2C%20a%20recent%20wargame%20found.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fdonald-trump-says-he-wont-quit-nato-if-europe-pays-its-way%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20NATO%20unless%20European%20allies%20contribute%20more%2C%20and%20should%20he%20carry%20it%20out%20Europe%20may%20decide%20to%20go%20it%20alone%20on%20defense%2C%20the%20game%20suggests.%20%26quot%3BA%20US%20policy%20of%20frustrating%20NATO%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20cause%20the%20alliance%20to%20collapse%2C%20with%20the%20EU%20as%20a%20candidate%20for%20eventually%20replacing%20NATO's%20ultimate%20function%20%E2%80%94%20defending%20Europe%20from%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Finley%20Grimble%2C%20the%20British%20defense%20expert%20who%20designed%20and%20ran%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpaxsims.wordpress.com%2F2024%2F04%2F11%2Fwargaming-the-effects-of-a-trump-presidency-on-nato%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egame%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20doesn't%20have%20to%20withdraw%20from%20NATO%20to%20imperil%20the%2075-year-old%20alliance.%20Technically%2C%20the%20US%20is%20barred%20from%20leaving%20NATO%20after%20Congress%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2F4360407-congress-approves-bill-barring-president-withdrawing-nato%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evoted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202023%20to%20prohibit%20withdrawal%20without%20congressional%20approval.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20game%20showed%20how%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20the%20presumptive%20Republican%20presidential%20nominee%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F10%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-russia-nato%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20that%20he'd%20encourage%20Russia%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20whatever%20the%20hell%20they%20want%26quot%3B%20with%20NATO%20allies%20who%20spend%20too%20little%20on%20their%20militaries%20%E2%80%94%20could%20undermine%20NATO%20simply%20by%20doing%20as%20little%20as%20possible%20to%20support%20the%20alliance.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Donald%20Trump%20can%20do%20is%20just%20really%20hollow%20out%20what%20NATO%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20Grimble%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHe%20doesn't%20need%20to%20leave%20NATO%20to%20ruin%20it.%20He%20can%20ruin%20it%20from%20within.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrimble%2C%20who%20has%20conducted%20wargames%20for%20the%20British%20government%2C%20conceived%20of%20this%20game%20after%20claims%20by%20former%20US%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2020%2F06%2F23%2Fbolton-book-trump-nato-ukraine-election%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJohn%20Bolton%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20talked%20then-President%20Trump%20out%20of%20withdrawing%20from%20NATO%20in%202018.%20He%20designed%20a%20tabletop%20simulation%20where%20the%20players%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20British%20specialists%20in%20defense%2C%20intelligence%20and%20foreign%20policy%20%E2%80%94%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20leaders%20of%20the%2032%20NATO%20nations%2C%20plus%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%3B%20China%20was%20played%20by%20the%20umpires.%20The%20US%20was%20played%20by%20an%20American%20who%20%26quot%3Bwas%20trying%20to%20enter%20into%20the%20psyche%20of%20Trump%2C%20which%20was%20no%20easy%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20Grimble%20recalled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrump%2C%20who%20faces%20criminal%20charges%20in%20four%20separate%20cases%2C%20has%20been%20criticized%20for%20sowing%20chaos%20in%20American%20politics.%20And%20chaos%20is%20exactly%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20game%20when%20the%20fictional%20Trump%20takes%20office%20in%20January%202025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20administration%20immediately%20attempts%20to%20broker%20a%20peace%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20without%20European%20help%20%E2%80%94%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia.%20After%20the%20mediation%20fails%2C%20Trump%20slashes%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20domino%20to%20fall.%20Trump%20then%20drastically%20reduces%20US%20participation%20in%20NATO%2C%20including%20redeployment%20of%2050%20percent%20of%20American%20military%20assets%20in%20Europe%2C%20where%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20US%20troops%20are%20based%2C%20to%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20theater.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20also%20institutes%20a%20new%20policy%20called%20%26quot%3Bdormancy.%26quot%3B%20This%20includes%20a%20variety%20of%20go-slow%20tactics%2C%20such%20as%20less%20US%20participation%20in%20NATO%20exercises.%20A%20particularly%20damaging%20move%20is%20to%20bar%20the%20Supreme%20Allied%20Commander%20Europe%20(SACEUR)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20second-highest%20military%20position%20in%20NATO%2C%20and%20always%20a%20US%20officer%20%E2%80%94%20from%20acting%20without%20prior%20consultation%20with%20Washington.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20SACEUR%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grimble.%20%26quot%3BSo%20he%20%5BSACEUR%5D%20can%20start%20slowing%20things%20down%2C%20or%20prevent%20things%20from%20happening.%20The%20US%20can%20just%20take%20the%20funding%20from%20NATO%20programs%20and%20they%20will%20collapse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%2C%20NATO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6424099eed593e00183f0682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20speaks%20during%20a%202019%20meeting%20with%20Nato%20Secretary%20General%20Jens%20Stoltenberg.%3Cp%3ENICHOLAS%20KAMM%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20game%20continued%2C%20the%20US%20complains%20that%20some%20NATO%20members%20are%20failing%20to%20meet%20the%20alliance's%20goal%20of%202%20percent%20of%20each%20nation's%20GDP%20on%20defense%20(the%20real-life%20Trump%20recently%20urged%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Ftrump-considering-3-per-cent-121651510.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E3%20percent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20The%20complaints%20are%20valid%3A%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20game%20in%202027%2C%20many%20members%20still%20hadn't%20reached%20the%202%20percent%20goal.%20Interestingly%2C%20while%20the%20US%20minimizes%20its%20presence%20in%20NATO%2C%20it%20does%20continue%20bilateral%20defense%20cooperation%20with%20the%20NATO%20members%20bordering%20Russia%2C%20including%20Finland%2C%20Romania%2C%20Poland%20and%20the%20Baltic%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENATO%20was%20created%20four%20years%20after%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20II%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20avoid%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20interwar%20years.%20American%20security%20guarantees%20have%20precluded%20European%20powers%20from%20re-arming%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20greater%20expenses%20borne%20by%20the%20US.%20But%20with%20this%20US%20security%20umbrella%20suddenly%20diminishing%20in%20the%20game%2C%20France%20and%20Germany%20call%20for%20the%20European%20Union%20to%20take%20over%20from%20NATO.%20This%20angers%20Poland%2C%20which%20saw%20this%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20French%20to%20kick%20the%20US%20out%20and%20to%20have%20France%20become%20the%20top%20military%20power%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20NATO%20members%20also%20quail%20at%20the%20thought%20that%20they%20might%20actually%20have%20to%20fight%20Russia%20without%20support%20from%20America%2C%20the%20most%20powerful%20NATO%20member%20given%20the%20size%20of%20its%20conventional%20forces%20and%20nuclear%20arsenal.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20Italy%2C%20for%20example%2C%20I'm%20certainly%20guaranteeing%20the%20security%20of%20Estonia%2C%26quot%3B%20Grimble%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20not%20really%20expecting%20to%20have%20to%20play%20such%20a%20prominent%20and%20crucial%20role%20in%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Czech%2C%20Norwegian%20and%20German%20soldiers%20take%20part%20in%20a%20NATO%20exercise%20in%20April.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e6064b4abc992e8c84cc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECzech%2C%20Norwegian%20and%20German%20soldiers%20take%20part%20in%20a%20NATO%20exercise%20in%20April.%3Cp%3EFlorian%20Gaertner%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Fjoint-expeditionary-force-global-britain-northern-europe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJoint%20Expeditionary%20Force%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20British-led%20military%20coalition%20of%2010%20Northern%20European%20nations%20that%20can%20operate%20independently%20of%20NATO%2C%20begins%20to%20make%20warfighting%20plans%20that%20assume%20there%20will%20be%20no%20NATO%20support.%20Turkey%20ponders%20whether%20to%20stay%20neutral%20%E2%80%94despite%20its%20NATO%20commitments%20%E2%80%94%20if%20Russia%20attacked%20the%20Baltic%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20with%20its%20campaign%20in%20Ukraine%20stalemated%2C%20Russia%20mulls%20invading%20the%20Baltic%20States%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20NATO%20members%20%E2%80%94%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20NATO%20disunity%20and%20perhaps%20split%20the%20alliance%20over%20willingness%20to%20risk%20war%20with%20Moscow.%20But%20the%20Russian%20player%20ultimately%20decides%20that%20Russia%20doesn't%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20fight%20Ukraine%20and%20occupy%20the%20Baltics%20%E2%80%94%20and%20invading%20NATO%20territory%20just%20might%20bring%20America%20back%20into%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20fictional%20Moscow%20does%20launch%20new%20offensives%20in%20Ukraine.%20Bereft%20of%20US%20support%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Europe%20is%20unable%20to%20compensate%20for%20%E2%80%94%20Ukraine%20feels%20compelled%20to%20sign%20a%20peace%20that%20cedes%20eastern%20Ukraine%20to%20Russia%20and%20installs%20a%20pro-Russian%20government%20in%20Kyiv.%20Europe%20faces%20another%20problem%3A%20fear%20that%20Russia%20might%20attack%20NATO%20is%20scaring%20off%20domestic%20and%20international%20investors%2C%20causing%20European%20economies%20to%20stumble.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20game%2C%20the%20effects%20of%20a%20US%20pullback%20from%20NATO%20are%20global.%20China%20realizes%20that%20the%20US%20has%20really%20shifted%20its%20focus%20from%20Europe%20to%20the%20Pacific%2C%20which%20deters%20Beijing%20from%20invading%20Taiwan.%20Yet%20this%20doesn't%20reassure%20Japan%2C%20Australia%20and%20South%20Korea%20%E2%80%94%20US%20allies%20whose%20forces%20and%20bases%20are%20essential%20to%20efforts%20to%20counter%20China%20%E2%80%94%20which%20worry%20that%20Trump%20might%20change%20his%20mind%20and%20abandon%20them%20too.%20Iran%20becomes%20emboldened%20to%20assert%20its%20power%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20which%20spurs%20an%20arms%20race%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20which%20left%20the%20British%20frustrated.%20The%20UK%20has%20traditionally%20backed%20a%20transatlantic%2C%20America-Europe%20alliance%20rather%20than%20a%20purely%20European%20defense%20bloc.%20Yet%20in%20the%20game%2C%20it%20could%20neither%20persuade%20Trump%20to%20ease%20his%20demands%2C%20nor%20the%20European%20NATO%20members%20to%20spend%20more%20on%20defense.%20%26quot%3BThe%20British%20felt%2C%20'for%20God's%20sakes%2C%20Trump%2C%20give%20the%20Europeans%20some%20time%2C'%26quot%3B%20Grimble%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20also%2C%20'Europeans%2C%20please%20do%20something.%20Let's%20all%20come%20to%20an%20accord%20and%20keep%20NATO%20alive.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWargaming%20experts%20always%20caution%20that%20games%20shouldn't%20be%20treated%20as%20predictors%20of%20the%20future%2C%20but%20only%20as%20experiments%20to%20explore%20possibilities.%20Nonetheless%2C%20this%20wargame%20seemed%20to%20confirm%20the%20worst%20fears%20of%20critics%20who%20believe%20Trump%20could%20destroy%20NATO%20and%20make%20Europe%20vulnerable%20to%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20had%20reduced%20its%20resourcing%20of%20the%20NATO%20deterrence%20and%20defense%20missions%2C%20meaning%20NATO%20did%20not%20have%20credible%20warfighting%20plans%20ready%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20Russian%20invasion%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grimble.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20thing%20had%20become%20dysfunctional.%20It%20certainly%20wasn't%20in%20any%20position%20to%20coherently%20defend%20against%20Russia%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20was%20a%20genuine%20desire%20to%20keep%20NATO%20alive.%20%26quot%3BMany%20NATO%20members%20%E2%80%94%20except%20for%20France%20mainly%20%E2%80%94%20thought%20post-Trump%20it%20could%20be%20salvageable%2C%26quot%3B%20Grimble%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20was%20necessary%20to%20keep%20the%20US%20in%2C%20keep%20it%20together%2C%20and%20rebuild%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%2