ent-pig-kidney-transplant-dies-2-months%2Fstory%3Fid%3D110139515%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20News%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Mass%20General%20transplant%20team%20is%20deeply%20saddened%20at%20the%20sudden%20passing%20of%20Mr.%20Rick%20Slayman.%20We%20have%20no%20indication%20that%20it%20was%20the%20result%20of%20his%20recent%20transplant%2C%26quot%3B%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERichard%20Slayman%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Weymouth%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20had%20battled%20Type%202%20diabetes%20and%20hypertension%20for%20years%20before%20receiving%20the%20transplant.%20Before%20the%20groundbreaking%20pig%20kidney%20transplant%2C%20Mr%20Slayman%20had%20a%20long%20history%20of%20managing%20Type%202%20diabetes%20and%20hypertension.%20He%20also%20relied%20on%20dialysis%20for%20several%20years%20before%20receiving%20a%20human%20kidney%20transplant%20in%20December%202018%2C%20performed%20by%20the%20same%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20transplanted%20kidney%20from%20the%20human%20donor%20functioned%20for%20about%20five%20years%20before%20showing%20signs%20of%20rejection.%20In%20May%202023%2C%20Mr.%20Slayman%20had%20to%20return%20to%20dialysis%20treatment%2C%20which%20significantly%20impacted%20his%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20according%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Slayman%20will%20forever%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20to%20countless%20transplant%20patients%20worldwide%20and%20we%20are%20deeply%20grateful%20for%20his%20trust%20and%20willingness%20to%20advance%20the%20field%20of%20xenotransplantation.%20We%20offer%20our%20heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20Mr%20Slayman's%20family%20and%20loved%20ones%20as%20they%20remember%20an%20extraordinary%20person%20whose%20generosity%20and%20kindness%20touched%20all%20who%20knew%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20hospital's%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kidney%20used%20in%20the%20transplant%20came%20from%20eGenesis%2C%20a%20Cambridge-based%20pharmaceutical%20company.%20This%20pioneering%20organ%20was%20harvested%20from%20a%20pig%20genetically%20modified%20using%20CRISPR-Cas9%20technology.%20According%20to%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital%2C%20the%20modification%20process%20involved%20removing%20incompatible%20pig%20genes%20and%20introducing%20specific%20human%20genes%20to%20enhance%20compatibility%20with%20the%20recipient's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20heartfelt%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Slayman's%20family%20expressed%20their%20deepest%20appreciation%20to%20the%20doctors%20and%20the%20entire%20care%20team%20at%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20family%20is%20deeply%20saddened%20about%20the%20sudden%20passing%20of%20our%20beloved%20Rick%20but%20take%20great%20comfort%20knowing%20he%20inspired%20so%20many.%20Millions%20of%20people%20worldwide%20have%20come%20to%20know%20Rick's%20story.%20We%20felt%20-%20and%20still%20feel%20-%20comforted%20by%20the%20optimism%20he%20provided%20patients%20desperately%20waiting%20for%20a%20transplant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20extremely%20grateful%20to%20his%20care%20team%20across%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital%20and%20Mass%20General%20Brigham%2C%20especially%20Dr%20Williams%2C%20Dr%20Kawai%2C%20and%20Dr%20Riella%2C%20who%20truly%20did%20everything%20they%20could%20to%20help%20give%20Rick%20a%20second%20chance.%20Their%20enormous%20efforts%20leading%20the%20xenotransplant%20gave%20our%20family%20seven%20more%20weeks%20with%20Rick%2C%20and%20our%20memories%20made%20during%20that%20time%20will%20remain%20in%20our%20minds%20and%20hearts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Slayman's%20family%20revealed%20that%20one%20of%20his%20driving%20forces%20behind%20the%20transplant%20was%20the%20desire%20to%20offer%20hope%20to%20the%20countless%20individuals%20battling%20end-stage%20organ%20failure%20and%20desperately%20waiting%20for%20a%20lifesaving%20transplant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRick%20accomplished%20that%20goal%20and%20his%20hope%20and%20optimism%20will%20endure%20forever.%20His%20legacy%20will%20be%20one%20that%20inspires%20patients%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20health%20care%20professionals%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715494260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdaos7tp_richard-slayman_625x300_12_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F62-year-old-who-received-first-ever-pig-kidney-transplant-dies-nearly-2-months-later-5644795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20sudden%20death%20remains%20unknown%2C%20the%20hospital%20has%20confirmed%20it%20was%20not%20related%20to%20the%20transplant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F62-year-old-who-received-first-ever-pig-kidney-transplant-dies-nearly-2-months-later-5644795%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F62-year-old-who-received-first-ever-pig-kidney-transplant-dies-nearly-2-months-later-5644795%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F62-year-old-who-received-first-ever-pig-kidney-transplant-dies-nearly-2-months-later-5644795%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98GenAI%20impact%20to%20be%20unimaginable%E2%80%99%20%3A%20TCS%20chairman%20makes%20observation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715493876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110049996%2Cimgsize-37616.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fgenai-impact-to-be-unimaginable-tcs-chairman-n-chandrasekaran-makes-important-observation%2Farticleshow%2F110049687.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22N%20Chandrasekaran%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20T