%20April%20and%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20big%20new%20chapter%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20life.%20The%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20the%20Japanese%20company%20added%20that%20the%20world%20needs%20Indian%20leadership%20and%20he%20is%20amazed%20by%20the%20diversity%20in%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BWorld%20needs%20Indian%20leadership.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20month%20since%20I%20moved%20to%20India%2C%20and%20once%20again%20I%20am%20amazed%20at%20the%20diversity%20of%20values%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20a%20miracle%20that%20India%20is%20one%20country%20despite%20being%20a%20large%20country%20with%20various%20religions%2C%20races%2C%20and%20values.%20It%20is%20a%20good%20opportunity%20to%20think%20about%20leadership%2C%20as%20India%20is%20in%20the%20election%20season%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Factivity-7190546282237628417-LnZH%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nishiyama%20also%20discussed%20the%20importance%20of%20collective%20effort%2C%20which%20helps%20bring%20new%20and%20diverse%20ideas.%20%26quot%3BIn%20socialist%20countries%20and%20military-like%20organizations%2C%20the%20traditional%20top-down%20approach%20has%20been%20effective.%20However%2C%20in%20today's%20unstable%20and%20uncertain%20society%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20move%20forward%20in%20a%20collaborative%20manner%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20diverse%20ideas.%20When%20a%20top-down%20approach%20is%20based%20solely%20on%20the%20ideas%20of%20a%20dictator%2C%20many%20blind%20spots%20occur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20also%20compared%20the%20working%20scenario%20between%20Japan%20and%20India.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BManagement%20in%20Japan%20has%20a%20nuanced%20connotation%20of%20locking%20other%20people%20into%20their%20own%20way%20of%20thinking%20and%20controlling%20them.%20Keep%20within%20the%20same%20one%20small%20framework.%20India%20is%20a%20large%20country%20with%20issues%20with%20neighboring%20countries%2C%20a%20history%20of%20independence%2C%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20religions%2C%20races%2C%20and%20values.%20Trying%20to%20confine%20ourselves%20to%20only%20one%20set%20of%20values%20will%20not%20work%20here.%20That%20is%20why%20they%20try%20to%20create%20a%20big%20framework%20that%20can%20include%20all%20things%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20instead%20of%20fitting%20different%20things%20into%20their%20one%20small%20framework.%20And%20each%20of%20them%20is%20able%20to%20move%20forward%20utilizing%20differences%2C%20although%20they%20are%20different%20individually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppreciating%20India's%20%26quot%3Bdiverse%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nishiyama%20said%20that%20it%20helps%20to%20move%20forward%20by%20creating%20a%20large%20plan%20which%20%26quot%3Bcan%20encompass%20heterogeneous%20values.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20it%20is%20different%20in%20Japan%20where%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhomogenous%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20asserted%20that%20India%20was%20capable%20of%20taking%20the%20lead%20in%20a%20global%20environment%20and%20that%20the%20country%20exemplified%20both%20competition%20and%20collaboration%2C%20citing%20the%20examples%20of%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20and%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella.%20%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20a%20chaotic%20place%2C%20with%20a%20diverse%20mix%20of%20values%20and%20power%20balance.%20It%20is%20definitely%20India%20that%20can%20move%20this%20forward.%20Because%20India%20has%20already%20experienced%20a%20lot%20of%20such%20things%20domestically.%20In%20the%20business%20field%2C%20Neither%20Sundar%20Pichai%20nor%20Satya%20Nadella%20are%20second-generation%20Americans.%20They%20were%20born%20in%20India%2C%20educated%20in%20India%2C%20and%20then%20went%20to%20the%20US%20for%20graduate%20school.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%20is%20only%20because%20India%20embodies%20both%20competition%20and%20collaboration%20that%20it%20is%20capable%20of%20leadership%20in%20a%20global%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcluding%20the%20post%2C%20Mr%20Nishiyama%20said%20that%20he%20will%20learn%20from%20Indian%20leadership%20and%20apply%20it%20to%20his%20organisation.%20He%20also%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20himself%20alongside%20an%20auto-rickshaw%20with%20a%20placard%20reading%20%26quot%3BWorld%20needs%20Indian%20leadership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20his%20post%20has%20amassed%20a%20lot%20of%20reactions%20on%20the%20networking%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndians%20have%20a%20knack%20for%20finding%20order%20in%20chaos%20%2C%20confusion%20%2C%20constraints%20and%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20techniques%20which%20Indian%20and%20Japanese%20can%20learn%20from%20each%20other%20and%20create%20a%20win%20win%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndians%20are%20good%20in%20leadership%20because%20of%20crisis%20handling%20capabilities%2C%20which%20is%20available%20in%20India%20everyday%20in%20abundance.%20On%20other%20hand%20Japanese%20are%20good%20in%20diligent%20leadership%20and%20hard%20working.%20Both%20countries%20has%20a%20lot%20great%20opportunities%20for%20collaboration%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20third%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715492760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Frajfgbk_japan-ceo-after-moving-to-bengaluru_625x300_12_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fworld-needs-indian-leadership-japan-ceo-after-moving-to-bengaluru-5644666%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Appreciating%20India's%20%26quot%3Bdiverse%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nishiyama%20said%20that%20it%20helps%20to%20move%20forward%20by%20creating%20a%20large%20plan%20which%20%26quot%3Bca