orry%20state%20of%20affairs%26quot%3B%20has%20continued%20because%20the%20earlier%20governments%20did%20not%20ensure%20Pakistan%20vacated%20the%20region%20after%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPoK%20has%20never%20been%20out%20of%20this%20country.%20It%20has%20always%20been%20a%20part%20of%20this%20country.%20There%20is%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20that%20PoK%20is%20very%20much%20a%20part%20of%20India.%20Now%2C%20how%20did%20other%20people%20get%20control%3F%20Ab%20ho%20jaata%20hai%20(it%20happens)%20when%20you%20have%20someone%20who%20is%20not%20a%20responsible%20custodian%20of%20a%20house%2C%20an%20outsider%20will%20come%20and%20steal%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20during%20an%20interactive%20session%20in%20Odisha's%20Cuttack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%20you%20have%20allowed%20another%20country...%20It%20was%20because%20we%20did%20not%20pursue%20the%20vacation%20of%20Pakistan%20from%20these%20territories%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20Independence%20that%20this%20very%20sorry%20state%20of%20affairs%20has%20continued.%20What%20will%20happen%20in%20the%20future%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20tell.%20But%2C%20I%20always%20tell%20people%20one%20thing%20that%20today%20PoK%20is%20in%20the%20consciousness%20once%20again%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20We%20had%20forgotten%20about%20it%2C%20we%20were%20made%20to%20forget%20about%20it%2C%20but%20it%20is%20back%20now%2C%20definitely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20blamed%20the%20previous%20Congress%20governments%20for%20several%20problems%20that%20had%20emerged%20on%20the%20foreign%20policy%20front%2C%20post%20Independence.%20A%20week%20earlier%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20he%20told%20a%20gathering%20that%20Sardar%20Patel%20had%20opposed%20India%20approaching%20the%20UN%20on%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%2C%20but%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20disregarded%20it.%3C%2F