s%20are%20encouraged%20to%20delve%20deeply%20into%20subjects%20of%20their%20choosing%20and%20conduct%20in-depth%20studies%20according%20to%20their%20interests%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children's%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmeen%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20living%20in%20Pathshala%20hostel%20and%20has%20been%20with%20Juin%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20shares%20his%20perspective%2C%20%EF%BF%BDThe%20most%20enriching%20aspect%20of%20our%20education%20is%20a%20class%20where%20we%20learn%20without%20textbooks.%20We%20select%20a%20topic%2C%20discuss%20it%2C%20and%20learn%20from%20each%20other%20and%20our%20teachers.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20educators%20stress%20on%20understanding%20concepts%20deeply%20rather%20than%20just%20memorisation.%EF%BF%BD%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn