0they%20spoke%20about%20everything%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20particularly%20food-forward%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20conversation%20was%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Singh%20toyed%20with%20the%20brilliant%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F223780%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-harsh-kedia-diabetic-chef-guilt-free-desserts-inspiring-india-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediabetic-friendly%20biscuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20%EF%BF%BD%20a%20rarity%20at%20the%20time%20%EF%BF%BD%20his%20grandaughter%20was%20amazed.%20%EF%BF%BDNow%20you%20know%20where%20I%20get%20it%20from%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20smiles%2C%20referring%20to%20her%20passion%20for%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MasterChef%20Australia%20Season%2016%20contestant%20may%20have%20traversed%20the%20world%2C%20but%20all%20roads%20have%20always%20led%20back%20home%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20household%20that%20witnessed%20a%20confluence%20of%20culture%20as%20the%20family%EF%BF%BDs%20Punjabi%20descent%20and%20love%20for%20%3Cem%3Erajma%20chawal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(red%20kidney%20beans%20in%20a%20thick%20gravy%20served%20with%20rice)%20blended%20with%20their%20occasional%20preference%20for%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20crepe%20made%20with%20fermented%20batter)%20and%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20savoury%20condiment).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20powerhouse%20of%20flavour%20that%20Saigal%20has%20been%20bringing%20to%20the%20MasterChef%20table%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20season.%20And%20her%20culinary%20prowess%20has%20been%20winning%20both%20palettes%20and%20hearts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20settles%20down%20for%20a%20t%EF%BF%BDte-%EF%BF%BD-t%EF%BF%BDte%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20where%20she%20shares%20the%20reciprocal%20relationship%20that%20she%EF%BF%BDs%20always%20shared%20with%20food%2C%20traces%20her%20steps%20back%20to%20the%20biggest%20influences%20in%20her%20life%2C%20and%20elaborates%20on%20how%20the%20dots%20connected%20to%20lead%20her%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292787%2Fmasterchef-australia-sandeep-pandit-revives-traditional-kashmiri-pandit-recipes-indian-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld%EF%BF%BDs%20most%20coveted%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%EF%BF%BDI%EF%BF%BDd%20say%20my%20paternal%20grandfather%20impacted%20my%20love%20for%20food%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20His%20ideas%20were%20almost%20like%20mind-benders%20for%20me.%20They%20caused%20me%20to%20think%20beyond%20the%20obvious.%EF%BF%BD%20An%20anecdote%20that%20sums%20up%20her%20%3Cem%3Edarji%EF%BF%BDs%3C%2Fem%3E%20out-of-the-box%20thinking%20is%20when%20on%20a%20shopping%20spree%20he%20picked%20up%20a%20bottle%20of%20ketchup%2C%20took%20a%20good%20look%20at%20the%20ingredients%20and%20said%2C%20%EF%BF%BDOh%2C%20we%20can%20make%20this%20at%20home!%EF%BF%BD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20his%20word%2C%20he%20spent%20the%20next%20many%20hours%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20experimenting%20to%20get%20the%20flavours%20right.%20And%20the%20result%20was%20pretty%20good%2C%20Saigal%20affirms.%20When%20he%20wasn%EF%BF%BDt%20prodding%20her%20to%20think%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20the%20ordinary%2C%20he%20was%20researching%20recipes%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%20And%20as%20grandfather%20and%20granddaughter%20sat%20down%20to%20dissect%20these%2C%20fascination%20flooded%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%EF%BF%BDI%20just%20was%20amazed%20at%20his%20thirst%20for%20knowledge%20and%20his%20hunger%20made%20me%20hungry%20to%20learn%20more%2C%EF%BF%BD%20she%20reminisces.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw