0If%20it%20retains%20its%20colour%2C%20it%EF%BF%BDs%20pure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20The%20Dal%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20the%20boiled%20paneer%20cool%20in%20water.%20Add%20some%20%3Cem%3Etoor%20dal%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20the%20water%20and%20let%20it%20rest%20for%2010%20minutes.%20If%20the%20water%20turns%20light%20red%2C%20the%20paneer%20may%20be%20contaminated.%20If%20the%20colour%20doesn%EF%BF%BDt%20change%2C%20go%20ahead%20and%20enjoy%20your%20paneer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20The%20Texture%20%26amp%3B%20Taste%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20%3Cem%3Epaneer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348039%2Fbest-organic-masalas-spices-in-india-mdh-everest-ethylene-oxide-satva-naturalland-organics-praakritik-himalaya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimply%20try%20and%20smell%3C%2Fa%3E%20(shouldn%EF%BF%BDt%20smell%20sour)%20it%20first.%20If%20it%EF%BF%BDs%20sold%20open%2C%20taste%20it.%20It%20should%20taste%20milky%20and%20be%20soft.%20If%20it%EF%BF%BDs%20too%20chewy%20or%20like%20rubber%2C%20you%20should%20refrain%20from%20buying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6dNaqpI60f%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6dNaqpI60f%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E